juke

::The horribly mutated human reacts to your presence partially with surprise, partially with anxiety. His off-centered eyes dart over you for any signs of hostility, and it becomes instantly apparent that the duo would bolt it even at a blink too sudden. He speaks after a short delay, concurrently delivering a dangerous dose of his foul, acrid breath to your face; it burns your nostrils as if he was lavaging them with a bottle of ammonia. After the initial distraction, you manage to focus on his words.::

We don't want no trouble and... ::wheeze:: we ain't got nothing... mrrr... ::He coughs.::
Mrrr?
Shoo...
Can you... understand me? ::wheeze::
Did the soup... ::wheeze:: attract you?
::Watches you.::
::Looks at Doubletap.::
context.npc_cc_juke_met
context.npc_cc_juke_met
Relax, I'm not here to rob you.
I'll be the judge of that. Stand aside - I'm searching this place.
Die, freak!
::He relaxes a bit and nods.::
Alright, alright. We won't try... ::wheeze:: to stop you, but there's... ::wheeze:: nothing to take.
What's in the soup?
What are you guys doing here?
Why do you live in the sewers?
Are there more of you... people here?
Jookhela?
How come you guys are still alive yet Jookhela killed everyone else?
I need to get the power going through this part of the sewers again. You got any idea where the power generator is?
I killed Jookhela.
I'll see you guys later.
I'm Juke... ::wheeze:: and this here is Doubletap. :: He coughs violently then spits aside.::
Stuff... ::He wheezes.::
We live here. ::He coughs.::
tempcontext.lastQ
And where should we live? ::He coughs.:: If we go up there... ::wheeze:: they'll shoot us... ::wheeze:: on sight.
There used to be, but... ::wheeze:: Jookhela got them all. Now it's just me and ol' Doubletap. ::He coughs and spits something green aside.::
Jookhela is... ::wheeze:: a *demon* rathound.
It's the *joojoo*... ::wheese:: junk incense.
Yes... ::wheeze:: It's east of here p--... ::He coughs.:: past the gate. But the gate... ::wheeze:: it is locked.

::He looks at you suspiciously.:: You did? If that... ::wheeze:: is the case you... ::wheeze:: might have saved our lives. We have nothing... ::wheeze:: to give you though. ::He coughs.:: Except our thanks.
Beware... ::wheeze:: of *Jookhela*.
Be careful out there... ::Wheezes.:: The traps... ::wheezes:: are for Jookhela... ::coughs:: not you.
Careful out there.
Feel free to... ::wheeze:: join us for some... ::wheeze:: barrel soup... ::coughs:: when it's done.
You do not... ::wheeze:: ask that... ::wheeze:: if you plan on eating it.
tempcontext.lastQ
If you... ::wheeze:: can call it that.
We used to... ::wheeze:: live in Junkyard, but... ::coughs:: scavengers kept busting in... ::wheeze:: killing us and taking our things. ::Coughs.:: Mrrr....
I know what--... ::coughs.:: what you think... ::wheeze:: you don't believe in demons. ::He coughs violently.:: Mrrr... neither did we before... ::wheeze:: we came here.
It is not the joojoo junk... ::Coughs.::
Grit had the key... ::wheeze:: but we haven't seen him... ::wheeze:: in a while.
Demons cannot... ::wheezes:: be killed. Only delayed... ::coughs:: by joojoo!
Whatever.
We came here thinking... ::wheeze:: it would be safer and... ::wheeze:: we could forage for more food.
This demon is... ::wheeze:: very real. Very. He stalks... ::wheeze:: the sewers, cunning like... ::coughs:: mrrr... Devil himself.
Mrrr... it is!
Jookhela got him probably. ::He coughs violently and spits aside.::
::He coughs violently.:: How wrong we were.
Sometimes he... ::wheeze:: sends his shadows at us. ::Coughs.:: They howl for hours... ::wheeze:: so we cannot sleep.
If you burn... ::wheeze:: the junk just the right... ::wheeze:: way and.. ::He coughs.:: say all the right words... ::wheeze:: it will ward off the demon.
He paralyzes his... ::wheeze:: victims with his mind... ::wheeze:: before devouring them alive. ::He coughs.:: Mrrr.
